  27 Mar 2015; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> nx-3.5.0.20.ebuild,
  nx-3.5.0.28.ebuild, nx-3.5.0.30.ebuild:
  No need to depend on libtirpc (yet), thanks F. Kater <fkater@googlemail.com>
  in bug #370767

*nx-3.5.0.30 (16 Mar 2015)

  16 Mar 2015; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> +nx-3.5.0.30.ebuild:
  Version bump

  18 Feb 2015; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> -nx-3.5.0.24.ebuild,
  -nx-3.5.0.27.ebuild, nx-3.5.0.28.ebuild, -files/nx-3.5.0.27-jpeg-9a.patch:
  Missing build dependency on x11-libs/libfontenc, thanks everyone in bug
  #536058. Remove some versions

